Title:
Login page refreshes and does not display error message after failed login

Environment:
Windows 10, Chrome v142.0

Steps to reproduce:

Go to the login page

Enter test@test.com in the email field

Enter 123 in the password field

Click the Login button

Expected result:
An error message "Invalid email or password" should appear and the page should not refresh.

Actual result:
The page refreshes and no error message is displayed.

Severity: High
Priority: Medium
